## 💰 Monetization

**Model:** Premium one-time purchase — **$4.99**
- No ads
- Players pay once, get the full game; demo allows only 8 hours of play
- Rationale: office workers have disposable income and hate manipulative monetization
- Possible future: No upfront cost + paid DLC expansions (new company types, scenarios)

