## 😤 Office Motivation & Fever Mode

**Office Motivation** is the collective energy/will of the entire office — renamed from "OfficeMorale" for clarity.

- Calculated as an aggregate of all individual employee morale scores
- Displayed as a 0–100% bar on the HUD
- Influences productivity, willingness to work, and performance across the board

**Fever Mode:**
- Triggers automatically when Office Motivation hits **100%**
- Duration: **5 minutes** (real time)
- Effect: **All stats doubled** for every employee
- Visual cue: Screen effect, music shift, excited animations
- After Fever Mode ends: Office Motivation drops to **50%**
- Rewards players who invest in morale-building facilities and events

