## 💼 Corporate Points System

Corporate Points are the in-game resource equivalent of "Research Points" in Kairosoft games.

**How they are earned:**
- Employees completing tasks
- Employees finishing projects
- Employees using facilities

**How they are spent:**
- **Shop** — buy items to boost employee stats
- **Training** — level up employees
- **Research menu** — win Donors, unlock new capabilities
- **Advertisement** — boost company reputation

**Training details:**
- Assign an employee to a training session
- Different job types have unique training perks
- Certain groups training together earn **bonus stats** (e.g., Procurement + Operations training together = logistics synergy bonus)
- Training outcomes are influenced by employee personality and current stats

