## 📊 Employee Stats & Task Matching

Each employee has a set of stats. Specific stats make them better suited to specific tasks.

**Example stats:**
| Stat | Description |
|---|---|
| Charm | Persuasion, client-facing tasks, donor acquisition |
| Focus | Deep work, report writing, research tasks |
| Energy | Overall stamina, sustaining long projects |
| Teamwork | Collaboration bonus, group project efficiency |
| Tech | IT, systems, technical project tasks |
| Operation | Admin, logistics, procurement tasks |

**Task-Stat matching examples:**
| Task | Primary Stat Required |
|---|---|
| Getting a Donor | Charm |
| Writing a Report | Focus |
| Procurement Run | Organization |
| System Setup | Technical |
| Team Workshop | Teamwork |

Employees with high matching stats complete tasks faster and with better quality output.

