## 🎯 Donor System (Planned — M4)

Donors are the NGO equivalent of winning major clients.
They represent real funding and unlock new content.

### How It Works
- Accessed via Corporate > Research
- Player spends Corporate Points to pursue a donor
- Additional requirements: minimum Reputation, employee stat thresholds
- Winning a donor unlocks:
  - Monthly funding added to cash automatically
  - Corporate Points bonus (one-time)
  - New projects tied to donor focus
  - Specific Hero employees (see Hero Roster)
  - Special items for Shop

