## 🏗️ Facility Combos

Facilities provide stat buffs to nearby employees. Placing specific facilities adjacent to each other activates **combo bonuses**.

**How combos work:**
- Shared resources can power multiple area effects simultaneously
- Example: A single **Coffee Machine** placed between a **Lazy Area** and a **Gossip Area** activates both area effects — the Coffee Machine gains the bonus of both combos
- Rewards thoughtful spatial planning without penalizing clever shared use

**Example combos:**
| Combo Name | Facilities Required | Bonus |
|---|---|---|
| Gossip Hub | Gossip Area + Cafeteria + Coffee Machine | Morale +5, Charm +3 |
| Focus Zone | Quiet Area + Company Library | Focus +8 |
| *(More combos to be designed during M3)* | | |

**Combo list** is accessible in-game via **Lists → Combo**.

