## 🕐 OT System

Employees work 08:00–16:00 by default.
Player can assign OT after 16:00 via Corporate > Assign Tasks.

| OT Level | Extra Hours | Productivity Bonus | Motivation Cost |
|---|---|---|---|
| None | +0 | 100% | 0/tick |
| Light OT | +2 hrs | +30% | -5/tick |
| Heavy OT | +4 hrs | +50% | -15/tick |
| Crunch | +8 hrs | +70% | -30/tick |

- If motivation reaches 0 → employee enters Burnout state
- Burnout: productivity -80%, spreads negativity to nearby employees
- Recovery: remove OT, motivation recovers +5/tick naturally
- Player must balance deadline pressure vs team wellbeing

