## 🏆 Hero Employee System

Hero Employees are legendary characters that can be unlocked through special conditions.
Once unlocked, they appear in the HireScreen candidate pool.

### Unlock Methods
- Special Events: certain random events trigger hero availability
- Donor Unlock: winning specific donors unlocks specific heroes
- Research: completing certain research paths unlocks heroes
- Ultimate Condition: Derek Anan Boonphun requires all three:
